{
    "id": "9b90cd45-4423-4a12-a585-a018f479810d",
    "documentation": "# Fynd Engage\n\nThis document outlines how to authenticate with Fynd Engage in Boltic using **API Key and Secret** authentication.\n\n## Authentication Type\n\n### Access Token\n\nFynd Engage uses an **Access Token** method based on your **API Key** and **API Secret**. These credentials are used to generate authorization headers that authenticate API requests.\n\n## Required Fields\n\n### API Key\n\n- **Description**: Your Fynd API Key.\n- **Where to Find**:  \n- **Login to Fynd Engage - Settings - Generate API KEY - Name API Key - API key and Secret is Generated** \n\n### API Secret\n\n- **Description**: Your Fynd API Secret.\n- **Where to Find**:  \n- **Login to Fynd Engage - Settings - Generate API KEY - Name API Key - API key and Secret is Generated** \n\n---\n\n",
    "integration_id": "146f9c48-92f7-49ff-9102-a08c28dc0eb1",
    "content": {
        "parameters": [
            {
                "meta": {
                    "value": "access_token",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "label": "Access Token",
                            "value": "access_token"
                        }
                    ],
                    "validation": {
                        "required": true
                    },
                    "description": "Choose the type of authentication you want to use.",
                    "displayName": "Authentication Type",
                    "displayType": "hidden",
                    "placeholder": "Select an authentication type"
                },
                "name": "type"
            }
        ],
        "access_token": {
            "validate": {
                "url": "https://api.engage.fynd.com/service/platform/v1/user/check-user",
                "body": {
                    "name": "{{secrets.name}}",
                    "email": "{{secrets.email}}",
                    "phone": "{{secrets.phone}}",
                    "userIdentifier": "{{secrets.userIdentifier}}"
                },
                "method": "post",
                "headers": {
                    "Content-Type": "application/json",
                    "Authorization": "Basic convertBufferBase64String({{secrets.api_key}}:{{secrets.api_secret}})"
                },
                "response": {
                    "error": {
                        "code": "{{response.status}}",
                        "message": "{{response.data.message}}"
                    },
                    "output": "{{response.data}}"
                }
            },
            "parameters": [
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "API Key is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "Refer to the Fynd API authentication documentation for detailed instructions on getting your API key.",
                        "displayName": "API Key",
                        "displayType": "text",
                        "placeholder": "Enter your API Key"
                    },
                    "name": "api_key"
                },
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "API Secret is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "Refer to the Fynd API authentication documentation for detailed instructions on getting your API secret.",
                        "displayName": "API Secret",
                        "displayType": "password",
                        "placeholder": "Enter your API Secret"
                    },
                    "name": "api_secret"
                },
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "Full Name is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "The full name of the user.",
                        "displayName": "Full Name",
                        "displayType": "text",
                        "placeholder": "Enter full name"
                    },
                    "name": "name"
                },
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "Email Address is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "The user's email address.",
                        "displayName": "Email Address",
                        "displayType": "email",
                        "placeholder": "Enter email address"
                    },
                    "name": "email"
                },
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "pattern": "^[0-9]{10}$",
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "Phone Number is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "The user's phone number.",
                        "displayName": "Phone Number",
                        "displayType": "text",
                        "placeholder": "Enter phone number"
                    },
                    "name": "phone"
                },
                {
                    "meta": {
                        "validation": {
                            "required": true,
                            "requiredDetail": {
                                "errorMsg": "User Identifier is required"
                            }
                        },
                        "description": "A unique identifier for the user.",
                        "displayName": "User Identifier",
                        "displayType": "text",
                        "placeholder": "Enter user identifier"
                    },
                    "name": "userIdentifier"
                }
            ]
        }
    },
